// CSS notes

3 types of CSS - Internal,External,Inline
1) Inline CSS 
- <html style = "background:blue">
</html>

- style is NAME
- background is PROPERTY and blue is VALUE of the PROPERTY

2) Internal CSS
<html>
  <head>
    <style>
      html{
          background:red;
          }
    </style>
  </head>
</html>

-Only for single-page websites
-for multiple-page websites use external css;

3)External CSS
<html>
  <head>
    <link>
        rel = "stylesheet"
        href ="./styles.css"
    />
  </head>
</html>

